I dunno, finally decided to login and update, alots been happening lately. I'll think of more to write later.

Long time since I updated, but anyway. Yea, I got the shard totally
ruling all. All shrines and death vortex's now work, cool NPC quests work
we have everything except newbie town stones!

Yea, word. I got Insomnia running, better than ever before. You only
wish you were as l33t as me. ;)

Well Well Well. The FreeBSD boxen now also hosts an IRCD foe me.
To access it, point your favorite IRC client to insomniauo.cjb.net:7000.
(7000 is the port.)
Good day, and I hope to see you on the server!

Well me and Brad finally got a stable FreeBSD box put up! Still
deciding what it's gonna host. Probably UO. w00t! Hope to see you
on the shard when it goes up!

Just letting everyone know I fixed my profile! LiveJournal
really is a miracle worker!
Just testing my new account out! :D
